License: UNKNOWN
Description: # Docker Healthchecker
        Wait for Docker healthchecks to be healthy
        
        ## Installation
        ```
        pip install docker-healthchecker
        ```
        
        ## Usage Examples
        ### Single container
        ```
        docker-healthchecker <container_id>
        ```
        
        ### Docker Compose
        ```
        docker-compose ps -aq | docker-healthchecker
        ```
        
